from ad482.common import steps
from labs.common.userinterface import Console
from labs.grading import Default as GuidedExercise


# TODO: Maybe better to delete this class
# if we dont have a usecase for this.
class DeleteKafka(GuidedExercise):
    __LAB__ = "delete-kafka"

    """
    Deletes the Kafka cluster
    """

    def start(self):
        items = [
            steps.check_ocp_api(),
            steps.check_ocp_credentials(),
            steps.move_to_kafka_cluster_namespace(),
            steps.delete_kafka_cluster(),
        ]
        Console(items).run_items(action="Cleaning")

    def finish(self):
        steps = []
        Console(steps).run_items(action="Finishing")
